          "category": "staff_qualifications",
          "text": "Iowa child care licensing — Following their first year of employment, all center directors and all staff must: (1) Maintain current certification for Iowa’s training for the mandatory reporting of child abuse; infant, child and adult CPR; and infant, child and adult first aid.",
